License placeholder for the CROP-3D paper artifact.

The intended release separates code, demo data, trained models, and media:

- Code: to be released under a permissive open-source license selected by the authors before public upload.
- Demo data: for research and review use, subject to final dataset permission review.
- Full dataset: not included in this repository; availability will be documented in `docs/dataset.md`.
- Model checkpoints and high-resolution videos: not included in this repository; links will be documented in `docs/model_weights.md` and the project README.

Before making this repository public, replace this placeholder with the final license text and confirm third-party license compatibility for 2DGS, COLMAP-related utilities, Depth Anything-derived components, and copied evaluation code.

